HEADWORD: Cyathophylloid
<hw>Cy`a*tho*phyl"loid</hw> <pr>(s?`?-th?-f?l"loid)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<ety>[NL. <ets>cyathophyllum</ets>, fr. Gr. <grk>ky`aqos</grk> a cup +
<grk>fy`llon</grk> a leaf.]</ety> <fld>(Paleon.)</fld> <def>Like, or
