==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Cyathophylloid
<hw>Cy`a*tho*phyl"loid</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Paleon.)</fld> <def>A
fossil coral of the family <fam>Cyathophyllid⟦ae⟧</fam>; sometimes
extended to fossil corals of other related families belonging to the
group Rugosa; -- also called <altname>cup corals</altname>. Thay are
found in paleozoic rocks.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Cycad</ent>⟦br⟧
